name: Accolades
description: I'm in the spotlight. With reverence and open arms I take in the moment and acknowledge those people and places that have been a part of the journey, and that have acknowledged the challenge. I thank myself for the beauty in each moment seen  in the spotlight and shadow's silence. A true Dance of Life unfolds and then we bow with reverence and thank our lucky stars. (Dance of Life Series 4 of 4)
